{"text_id":259537,"tokens":["We"," present"," a"," new"," algorithm"," for"," spectral"," clustering"," based"," on"," a"," column","-","p","ivo","ted"," QR"," factorization"," that"," may"," be"," directly"," used"," for"," cluster"," assignment"," or"," to"," provide"," an"," initial"," guess"," for"," k","-","means"," ."," Our"," algorithm"," is"," simple"," to"," implement",","," direct",","," and"," requires"," no"," initial"," guess","."," Furthermore",","," it"," scales"," linearly"," in"," the"," number"," of"," nodes"," of"," the"," graph"," and"," a"," randomized"," variant"," provides"," significant"," computational"," gains","."," Provided"," the"," subspace"," spanned"," by"," the"," eigenvectors"," used"," for"," clustering"," contains"," a"," basis"," that"," resembles"," the"," set"," of"," indicator"," vectors"," on"," the"," clusters",","," we"," prove"," that"," both"," our"," deterministic"," and"," randomized"," algorithms"," recover"," a"," basis"," close"," to"," the"," indicators"," in"," Fro","ben","ius"," norm","."," We"," also"," experimentally"," demonstrate"," that"," the"," performance"," of"," our"," algorithm"," tracks"," recent"," information"," theore","tic"," bounds"," for"," exact"," recovery"," in"," the"," stochastic"," block"," model","."," Finally",","," we"," explore"," the"," performance"," of"," our"," algorithm"," when"," applied"," to"," a"," real"," world"," graph","."],"sub_source":"sci_gen","model":"human","label":0}